Alembic migration environment for LeadForge.

Migrations run programmatically via `leadforge init` (see
leadforge.database.migrate.run_migrations). The connection URL comes from
DATABASE_URL / Settings (README §20), not from alembic.ini.

To create a new migration during development, from the repo root:

    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"

alembic.ini (repo root) points script_location here.
